- Added option to change twitter question
- Fixed small bugs

1.6.0.2 - 12/12/09
- Added close button in options page
- Added option to change tweet font-size and text shadow
- Added option to change URL Shortener
- Added more URL Shorteners (migre.me, bit.ly, j.mp, is.gd)
- Fixed favorites requests error

1.6.0.1 - 11/12/09
- Finished Favorites timeline
- Added API Requests number and porcentage for all timelines refresh time (need be fixed)
- Started implementing URL Longer (http://untr.im)

1.5.8 - 10/12/09
- Implemented Mentions/Messages/Favorites
